						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the Hiremaṭha.</p>						

						<p>15th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription indifferently engraved is dated the year Tā[ra]ṇa, Āśvija ba; the Śaka year is not given.</p>						

						<p>It mentions a gift made to the <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> of Pañchāksharadēva. The characters belong to the 15th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
